title: Sports Illustrated and Go RVing Tailgate Tour: College Station
text:
11:00 a.m. Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015 Categories 
Events, On Campus | Alumni, Sports Join Sports Illustrated and GoRVing at Kyle Field this Saturday to get pumped up for Alabama to take on the Texas A&M Aggies! Where? Texas A&M Fan Zone, corner of Houston St. and Joe Routt Blvd. When? 11:00AM â€“ 2:30PM CST What? - Chalk talk and autograph session with Dat Nguyen - Live demos and free food from local celeb chef Christopher Lampo - Interactive quarterback simulator - Get your picture on the cover of Sports Illustrated - Dometic cooler giveaways, tailgate games, and more! Visitors onsite and online will have a chance to win the ultimate RV tailgate and 15 tickets to a 2016 college football game of their choice. Follow along with #RVTailgateTour as we travel across the country all season long. For contest entry: https://promotions.si.com/4gn
